12:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"埼玉文化艺术活动列表2025 - 传统文化体验·艺术节·博物馆特展·野外电影完整攻略指南 | 关东旅游指南"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"埼玉县2025年文化艺术活动完整指南，深入了解川越传统文化体验、艺术节、博物馆特展、美术展览、野外电影等多样化艺术活动。提供详细的举办时间、观赏地点、活动特色、参与方式，体验埼玉地区丰富的文化艺术魅力，感受小江戸川越的历史文化传承。"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"author","content":"关东旅游指南团队"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"keywords","content":"埼玉文化艺术,川越传统文化,艺术节,博物馆特展,美术展览,野外电影,埼玉艺术活动,2025艺术展,埼玉旅游,日本文化艺术,小江戸川越,秩父夜祭,传统工艺,现代艺术,文化体验"}],["$","meta","4",{"name":"creator","content":"关东旅游指南"}],["$","meta","5",{"name":"publisher","content":"关东旅游指南"}],["$","meta","6",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","meta","7",{"name":"googlebot","content":"index, follow, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"category","content":"旅游"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"classification","content":"旅游指南"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"theme-color","content":"#3b82f6"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"msapplication-TileColor","content":"#3b82f6"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"mobile-web-app-capable","content":"yes"}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style","content":"default"}],["$","link","14",{"rel":"canonical","href":"http://localhost:3000/saitama/culture/"}],["$","meta","15",{"property":"og:title","content":"埼玉文化艺术活动列表2025 - 传统文化体验·艺术节·博物馆特展·野外电影完整攻略指南"}],["$","meta","16",{"property":"og:description","content":"埼玉县2025年文化艺术活动完整指南，川越传统文化体验、艺术节、博物馆特展、野外电影等多样化艺术活动等您来体验。感受埼玉地区丰富的文化艺术魅力。"}],["$","meta","17",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://www.kanto-travel-guide.com/saitama/culture"}],["$","meta","18",{"property":"og:site_name","content":"关东旅游指南"}],["$","meta","19",{"property":"og:locale","content":"zh_CN"}],["$","meta","20",{"property":"og:image","content":"http://localhost:3000/images/culture/saitama-culture.svg"}],["$","meta","21",{"property":"og:image:width","content":"1200"}],["$","meta","22",{"property":"og:image:height","content":"630"}],["$","meta","23",{"property":"og:image:alt","co